statements: SELECT * FROM rehabilitation_exercises WHERE exercise_type = 'Stretching';
SELECT exercise_name, exercise_description, tutorial_link FROM rehabilitation_exercises WHERE exercise_type = 'Strength Training';
SELECT exercise_name, tutorial_link FROM rehabilitation_exercises WHERE exercise_type = 'Balance';
SELECT exercise_name, exercise_description FROM rehabilitation_exercises WHERE created_at > '2021-01-01';
SELECT exercise_id, exercise_name FROM rehabilitation_exercises WHERE exercise_type = 'Stretching' ORDER BY exercise_id DESC;
SELECT * FROM rehabilitation_exercises WHERE exercise_type = 'Strength Training' ORDER BY exercise_name DESC;
SELECT exercise_id, exercise_name, exercise_description FROM rehabilitation_exercises WHERE exercise_type = 'Balance' LIMIT 5;
SELECT exercise_id, exercise_name, tutorial_link FROM rehabilitation_exercises WHERE exercise_type = 'Stretching' AND exercise_description IS NOT NULL;
SELECT exercise_id, exercise_name, EXTRACT(YEAR FROM created_at) AS year_created FROM rehabilitation_exercises ORDER BY year_created DESC;
SELECT * FROM rehabilitation_exercises WHERE exercise_type IN ('Stretching', 'Balance') ORDER BY created_at ASC LIMIT 10;
SELECT exercise_name, difficulty_level, target_area FROM exercises;
SELECT * FROM exercises WHERE difficulty_level > 3;
SELECT exercise_name, description FROM exercises ORDER BY exercise_name ASC;
SELECT * FROM exercises WHERE target_area = 'Legs' AND difficulty_level < 4;
SELECT exercise_name, difficulty_level, target_area FROM exercises WHERE difficulty_level = (SELECT MAX(difficulty_level) FROM exercises);
SELECT * FROM exercises WHERE difficulty_level > 2;
SELECT exercise_name, target_area FROM exercises ORDER BY exercise_name DESC;
SELECT exercise_name, target_area, difficulty_level FROM exercises WHERE target_area = 'Legs';
SELECT exercise_name, description FROM exercises WHERE difficulty_level BETWEEN 1 AND 3;
SELECT exercise_name, difficulty_level FROM exercises JOIN progress_reports ON exercises.exercise_id = progress_reports.exercise_id WHERE progress_reports.intensity_level >= 5;
SELECT * FROM exercises;
SELECT exercise_id, exercise_name FROM exercises WHERE difficulty_level = 2;
SELECT exercise_name, description FROM exercises ORDER BY exercise_name DESC;
SELECT * FROM progress_reports WHERE duration_min > 30;
SELECT user_id, username FROM users ORDER BY user_id ASC;
SELECT * FROM users;
SELECT exercise_name, difficulty_level FROM exercises ORDER BY difficulty_level DESC;
SELECT username, email, date_joined FROM users WHERE date_joined > '2022-01-01';
SELECT u.username, e.exercise_name, pr.date_completed FROM users u JOIN progress_reports pr ON u.user_id = pr.user_id JOIN exercises e ON pr.exercise_id = e.exercise_id;
SELECT exercise_name, difficulty_level, description FROM exercises WHERE difficulty_level BETWEEN 2 AND 5;
SELECT * FROM Users;
SELECT user_name, date_of_birth FROM Users WHERE rehabilitation_goal = 'Knee Injury';
SELECT exercise_name, difficulty_level FROM RehabExercises ORDER BY difficulty_level DESC;
SELECT user_name, count(report_id) as total_reports FROM Users JOIN ProgressReports ON Users.user_id = ProgressReports.user_id GROUP BY Users.user_name;
SELECT user_name, exercise_name, performance_rating FROM Users JOIN ExerciseHistory ON Users.user_id = ExerciseHistory.user_id ORDER BY performance_rating DESC;
SELECT exercise_name, difficulty_level, target_muscle_group FROM RehabExercises WHERE difficulty_level > 3 ORDER BY exercise_name DESC;
SELECT user_name, date_of_birth, rehabilitation_goal FROM Users WHERE DATE_PART('year', date_of_birth) < 1990;

SELECT exercise_name, difficulty_level, target_muscle_group, user_name FROM RehabExercises JOIN ExerciseHistory ON RehabExercises.exercise_id = ExerciseHistory.exercise_id JOIN Users ON ExerciseHistory.user_id = Users.user_id WHERE difficulty_level BETWEEN 1 AND 3 ORDER BY user_name, difficulty_level DESC;
SELECT user_name, SUM(duration_in_minutes) AS total_duration FROM Users JOIN ProgressReports ON Users.user_id = ProgressReports.user_id GROUP BY user_name HAVING total_duration > 120;

SELECT exercise_name, COUNT(*) AS total_completed FROM RehabExercises JOIN ExerciseHistory ON RehabExercises.exercise_id = ExerciseHistory.exercise_id WHERE Completion_date BETWEEN '2022-01-01' AND '2022-12-31' GROUP BY exercise_name ORDER BY total_completed DESC;
SELECT * FROM exercises;
SELECT exercise_name, description FROM exercises WHERE body_part = 'Legs';
SELECT * FROM progress_reports WHERE completion_status = true;
SELECT user_id, username, age FROM users ORDER BY age DESC;
SELECT name, specialty FROM therapists WHERE specialty != 'Physical Therapy';
SELECT * FROM exercises ORDER BY exercise_name ASC;
SELECT exercise_id, description FROM exercises WHERE body_part = 'Legs';
SELECT user_id, username, age FROM users WHERE gender = 'Female' AND age > 30;
SELECT session_id, date_time, duration FROM sessions WHERE therapist_id = 3 ORDER BY date_time DESC;

SELECT exercises.exercise_name, progress_reports.date, progress_reports.completion_status FROM exercises JOIN progress_reports ON exercises.exercise_id = progress_reports.exercise_id ORDER BY progress_reports.date DESC;
